title: How rare are my skins?
body:
Okay so here is a list of the skins I currently have and I was just wondering how much my account would be worth roughly and which skins are the rarest!! please help me and thank you in advanced 
**Akali**- Crimson Akali, Nurse Akali And Bloodmoon Akali.
**Alistar**- Unchained Alistar.
**Annie**- Red Riding Annie And FrankenTibbers Annie.
**Ashe**- Freijord Ashe, Amethyst Ashe And Heartseeker Ashe.
**Blitz**- Definitely Not blitz And Riot Blitz.
**Caitlyn**- Artic Warefare Caitlyn And Officer Caitlyn.
**Cassiopeia**- Siren Cassiopeia And Mythic Cass.
**Diana**- Dark Valkyrie Diana.
**Evelynn**- Shadow Eve And Masquerade Eve.
**Fiora**- Royal Guard Fiora, Nightraven Fiora And Headmistress Fiora.
**Irelia**- Nightblade Irelia, Aviator Irelia, Infiltrator Irelia And Frostblade Irelia.
**Karma**- Traditional Karma.
**Katarina**- Mercenary Katarina, Bilgewater Katarina, Kitty cat Kat, High Command Katarina And Slay Bella Katarina.
**Kayle**- Judgment Kayle.
**Leblanc**- Prestigious Leblanc And Mistletoe Leblanc.
**Leona**- Valkyrie Leona.
**Lux**- Spelltheif Lux And Cammando Lux.
**Master Yi**- Samurai Yi.
**MIss Fortune**- Cowgirl MF, Waterloo MF, Secret Agent MF, Candy Cane MF, Road Warrior MF And Arcade MF.
**Nami**- Deep Sea Nami.
**Nidalee**- Snow Bunny Nidalee, Leopard Nidalee, Pharaoh Nidalee, Bewitching Nidalee And Super galaxy Nidalee.
**Nocturne**- Haunting Nocturne.
**Quinn**- Phoenix Quinn.
**Riven**- Redeemed Riven, Crimson Elite Riven And Battle Bunny Riven.
**Sejuani**- Sabretusk Sejuani And Traditional Sejuani.
**Shyvana**- Ironscale Shyvana and Boneclaw Shyvana.
**Sivir**- Spectacular Sivir, PAX sivir, Snowstorm Sivir and Neo PAX sivir.
**Soraka**- Divine Soraka.
**Tristana**- Riot Girl Tristana.
**Vayne**- Dragonslayer Vayne and Heartseeker Vayne.
**Vi**- Officer Vi.
**Zyra**- Wildfire Zyra.
